# Secrets and credential files.
#
# The .env entry above covers the canonical secrets file. The
# explicit OPENROUTER_API_KEY pattern below is a defensive
# marker so a future maintainer cannot accidentally remove the
# intent without seeing the rationale. The key is read from
# the environment at adapter construction time
# (`OpenRouterAdapter` raises if it is missing); it is never
# stored on disk by the project, but if a future debug script
# dumps the literal token into a file, the patterns below
# ensure the file is still excluded from version control.
#
# NB: ``.env.*`` is intentionally NOT listed here so that
# ``.env.example`` (and any future ``.env.sample``) can be
# committed. The literal ``.env`` line above is the only
# gitignore rule that covers the populated secrets file.
*.secret
*sk-or-v1-*.key
*OPENROUTER_API_KEY*

